cu.explanation_en: Setting the SST to an out-of-range value of 999 will cause PLMN configuration errors and network slice selection failures.

du.explanation_en: Setting the absolute SSB frequency to an excessively high value of 999999999 will cause invalid frequency configuration and SSB transmission failures.
du.explanation_zh: 將絕對 SSB 頻率設定為過高的 999999999 值會導致無效頻率配置，並造成 SSB 傳輸失敗。
